title: McCarthy gives Boehner a B- as he campaigns to replace him
text: > Top News McCarthy gives Boehner a B- as he campaigns to replace him Outgoing House Speaker John Boehner of Ohio, and House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy of Calif., interact during a new conference on Capitol Hill in Washington, Tuesday, Sept. 29, 2015. McCarthy is assuring Republicans he can bring them together, even as emboldened conservatives maneuver to yank their party to the right in the wake of the leader of the U.S. House of Representatives Speaker John Boehner's sudden resignation. (AP Photo/Carolyn Kaster)
